		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The program for your game is called the source, you put your file name there that you want to make into a NES rom. save those 2 lines into a BAT file by saving from notepad, and clicking save as ALL FILES and typing in NAME.BAT in the file name area.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
